n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"3cda5a00a227febc661820ce25594977cc5759b7","tid":1539042,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"#Chinazi"},{"pid":"660e5196976cac21615e6e7b2b8afa94f351cf69","tid":1539042,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"#Chinazi"},{"pid":"79a247cf42e8300dff80add894a492c8beb22c59","tid":1539042,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"#chinazi"},{"pid":"065b4417dd5cf4987001fcf377c4d9826d76b189","tid":1539042,"uid":274531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:06.000Z","msg":"612 721 728 805 811 831"},{"pid":"57cd10b13ed97e0044aee2686c03624f9855c51d","tid":1539042,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"612 721 728 805 811 831"},{"pid":"1749a0cd1d1a9aedeafcff32f17139bd70e21e4e","tid":1539042,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"}]}